ON> U.N. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Security </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Council </ORGANIZATION> and has only been recognized by <LOCATION> Turkey </LOCATION>. The Turkish Cypriots took no part in the election. The new president will be sworn in next Sunday.
